# Custom Suricata Detection Rules

This folder contains custom Suricata signatures developed during my SOC laboratory project.

## Rules Included

### HTTP Admin URI Detection
Detects HTTP requests containing the keyword "admin" within the URI.

### Suspicious ICMP Payload Detection
Detects ICMP packets containing a predefined hexadecimal payload pattern.

### SQL Injection Detection
Uses PCRE to identify common SQL injection characters and payloads within HTTP POST requests.

### ICMP Flood Detection
Triggers an alert when five ICMP packets are received from the same source within ten seconds.

### ICMP Rate Limiting
Demonstrates threshold-based alert suppression by limiting alerts to one every ten seconds per source.
